{"tid":1306782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁美芬呼籲公眾不要仇警、擾亂社會安寧和各區居民，停止任何暴力行為。","createTime":"2019-07-11T09:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T12:58:41.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"440428def0c678de891f17810a8e910d4b5b9337","tid":1306782,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:37:06.000Z","msg":"關注通識教育聯席會議召集人、經民聯立法會議員梁美芬表示，最近與教育局長楊潤雄會面，表達對通識科的意見，認為不應列為必修科，因目前科目範圍太大太難，雜亂無章，令不少學生感到吃力，強調並非因近期發生政治爭議找代罪羔羊。梁美芬又透露，早前約見學校課程檢討專責小組但被拒。<br />\n<br />\n對於有反對修訂《逃犯條例》的市民在社區設連儂牆，被持不同意見人士襲擊，梁美芬認為爭議應該停止，指不願見到任何暴力，包括衝擊立法會或群眾之間鬥爭，又呼籲公眾不要仇警，亦不要擾亂社會安寧和各區居民，停止任何暴力行為。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2397747/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2397747%2F&d=i5E3ds%2FeSPFE00WLmt852w9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=00b17a43\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2397747/</a>"},{"pid":"022d58a6f49d57bb415a2851da63b7a1c502e52b","tid":1306782,"uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:39:31.000Z","msg":"仲講通識<br />\n死唔斷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c649879c44a9d4346221d7ce748ceae98dddc3b","tid":1306782,"uid":28195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"仇鼠得唔得？"},{"pid":"85a0acd72907af8f20b96a76ef835b81a4c119a6","tid":1306782,"uid":202876,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"公眾呼籲梁美芬不要諉過於通識科, 不要不分是非黑白, 不要奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e491b787a9a3c1f2461bf7e29095a33af0965110","tid":1306782,"uid":189109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T09:40:59.000Z","msg":"公眾呼籲民建聯，工聯會，經民聯所有議員立即辭職"},{"pid":"64f83625cf91b68316735cfaa7122eda8c636dca","tid":1306782,"uid":23098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07